title: Best of The Program | Guests: Bill O'Reilly & Tabari Wallace | 5/8/20
description:
This month of job losses was the worst since 1945. We’re now sitting at 14.7% unemployment, but which jobs will return? Bill O’Reilly joins to discuss the latest: The DOJ drops the case against Michael Flynn, and James Comey isn’t happy. North Carolina principal Tabari Wallace joins to discuss how he made sure his seniors had a moment to remember.
